title: detective conan movie 6 - phatom of the baker street
description: Conan, Ai, Ran and The Detective Boys are 6 out of the 50 chosen kids to try a new virtual reality game. Conan and his friends enter London in the 1800 century. But soon after all the kids head into the game, Noah&#039;s Ark (A highly developed AI program) closes all exits to the game. Now the innocent game is a matter of life and death. If the kids don&#039;t finish the game, they&#039;re all going to die. One by one the kids "die" in the game, and Conan & co have to solve the puzzle to find out who can catch Jack The Ripper and save them all.
